{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/lentejas-de-verduras/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"A pizcas y a mizcas"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"831ad593-b0fc-5d19-80ff-ca5b58172e7e","excerpt":"Ahora que ha empezado el frío ya nos apetecen los platos de cuchara calentitos. Y siguiendo la receta de Mati, que ella misma heredó de su madre, hemos hecho…","html":"<p>Ahora que ha empezado el frío ya nos apetecen los platos de cuchara calentitos. Y siguiendo la receta de <strong>Mati</strong>, que ella misma heredó de su madre, hemos hecho lentejas de verduras al estilo tradicional. Además estas son ligeritas… rico, rico, sano, sano!!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 300px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/39b946e49777df09cc9522db0004d629/f93b5/IMG_7031-pizcas-300x225.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG 7031 pizcas 300x225\"\n        title=\"IMG_7031 pizcas\"\n        src=\"/static/39b946e49777df09cc9522db0004d629/f93b5/IMG_7031-pizcas-300x225.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/39b946e49777df09cc9522db0004d629/ff44c/IMG_7031-pizcas-300x225.jpg 158w,\n/static/39b946e49777df09cc9522db0004d629/f93b5/IMG_7031-pizcas-300x225.jpg 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Ingredientes para 4 personas:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 calabacín</li>\n<li>2 zanahorias</li>\n<li>2  patatas</li>\n<li>2 puerros</li>\n<li>1 cebolla</li>\n<li>4 ajos</li>\n<li>2 hojas de laurel</li>\n<li>350 gr lentejas pardinas</li>\n<li>Aceite</li>\n<li>Sal</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Pelamos y troceamos a daditos todas las verduras. Añadimos las hojas de laurel, los ajos pelados, las lentejas, sal (al gusto) y aceite (aproximadamente 3 cucharadas soperas).</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 300px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4123cfa06b96cc34930aa4ca92bd4927/f93b5/IMG_7032-pizcas-300x225.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG 7032 pizcas 300x225\"\n        title=\"IMG_7032 pizcas\"\n        src=\"/static/4123cfa06b96cc34930aa4ca92bd4927/f93b5/IMG_7032-pizcas-300x225.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4123cfa06b96cc34930aa4ca92bd4927/ff44c/IMG_7032-pizcas-300x225.jpg 158w,\n/static/4123cfa06b96cc34930aa4ca92bd4927/f93b5/IMG_7032-pizcas-300x225.jpg 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 300px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8ca15bddc3ed2084ff178486986477b3/f93b5/IMG_7033-pizcas-300x225.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG 7033 pizcas 300x225\"\n        title=\"IMG_7033 pizcas\"\n        src=\"/static/8ca15bddc3ed2084ff178486986477b3/f93b5/IMG_7033-pizcas-300x225.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8ca15bddc3ed2084ff178486986477b3/ff44c/IMG_7033-pizcas-300x225.jpg 158w,\n/static/8ca15bddc3ed2084ff178486986477b3/f93b5/IMG_7033-pizcas-300x225.jpg 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Añadimos agua fría  hasta cubrir todo el contenido. Ponemos el fuego al máximo hasta que empiece a hervir. Una vez que haya llegado a ebullición poner a fuego lento durante media hora. Transcurrido ese tiempo comprobar el estado de las lentejas, si no estuvieran blandas, dejaríamos otros 10 minutos más. Removemos de vez en cuando.</p>\n<p>Comprobar el punto de sal y servir.</p>\n<p>A nosotros nos gusta con estas verduras pero también se puede añadir pimiento rojo o verde. Depende de gustos.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/093a22bad36cabc187f1db48e9c07529/c08c5/IMG_7038-pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG 7038 pizcas\"\n        title=\"IMG_7038 pizcas\"\n        src=\"/static/093a22bad36cabc187f1db48e9c07529/828fb/IMG_7038-pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/093a22bad36cabc187f1db48e9c07529/ff44c/IMG_7038-pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/093a22bad36cabc187f1db48e9c07529/a6688/IMG_7038-pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/093a22bad36cabc187f1db48e9c07529/828fb/IMG_7038-pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/093a22bad36cabc187f1db48e9c07529/c08c5/IMG_7038-pizcas.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Lentejas de verduras","date":"November 16, 2011","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/una-cena-desde-la-otra-orilla-del-mediterraneo-kebab-y-falafel-caseros/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Una cena desde la otra orilla del Mediterráneo (Kebab y Falafel caseros...)"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/visita-al-mercado-central-de-valencia/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Visita al Mercado Central de Valencia"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"831ad593-b0fc-5d19-80ff-ca5b58172e7e","previousPostId":"45603f3d-71b7-538a-bf41-519c1bfb5a4d","nextPostId":"c6ba0edd-ce14-5e91-a88f-812eead590cc"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}